1
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:45,770
[Love of the Divine Tree]

2
00:01:46,670 --> 00:01:49,030
[Episode 7]

3
00:01:50,259 --> 00:01:51,450
No thanks...

4
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,420
The fortune teller

5
00:01:54,590 --> 00:01:56,870
said I'm born a jinx to my family

6
00:01:57,100 --> 00:01:58,060
and teachers.

7
00:01:58,460 --> 00:01:59,720
It's for your own good.

8
00:01:59,740 --> 00:02:01,540
Kneel and take me as your master.

9
00:02:05,110 --> 00:02:06,350
What's wrong with you?

10
00:02:06,350 --> 00:02:07,590
How can you get others to kneel?

11
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:09,190
Will you kneel if I ask you to?

12
00:02:11,130 --> 00:02:12,850
Sov... Sovereign Su.

13
00:02:13,580 --> 00:02:15,110
Why are you really on your knees?

14
00:02:15,110 --> 00:02:16,420
I wasn't serious.

15
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:19,070
The jade tablet is the Westers' sacred object.

16
00:02:19,070 --> 00:02:19,740
Are there still

17
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:21,740
remnants of Mu Qingge's authority?

18
00:02:22,740 --> 00:02:23,460
Go away!

19
00:02:29,540 --> 00:02:30,190
My Lord!

20
00:02:32,630 --> 00:02:34,110
We have help.

21
00:02:36,190 --> 00:02:37,190
Okay.

22
00:02:37,740 --> 00:02:39,579
Let's see how long you can hide.

23
00:02:47,350 --> 00:02:49,680
Her authority is really hard to overcome.

24
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,230
The jade tablet

25
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:58,460
is really something.

26
00:02:58,870 --> 00:03:00,800
It's like it can control Su Yishui.

27
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:10,110
Right!

28
00:03:10,540 --> 00:03:11,340
Maybe it could

29
00:03:11,390 --> 00:03:13,120
command him to save the people.

30
00:03:14,460 --> 00:03:15,150
Su Yishui.

31
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:16,829
Go and save the people—

32
00:03:22,940 --> 00:03:23,740
You can leave.

33
00:03:24,670 --> 00:03:25,670
But I guess

34
00:03:26,190 --> 00:03:27,700
that within 15 minutes,

35
00:03:28,070 --> 00:03:29,300
Wei Jiu will turn your friends

36
00:03:29,300 --> 00:03:30,560
into a pillar of smoke.

37
00:03:33,070 --> 00:03:34,070
Immortal Master.

38
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:35,380
Please save them.

39
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:36,829
Then first,

40
00:03:37,390 --> 00:03:38,650
take me as your master.

41
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:43,540
Immortal Master.

42
00:03:43,540 --> 00:03:45,260
You look like a righteous man.

43
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,960
You won't just let them die.

44
00:03:47,070 --> 00:03:47,870
Come to think of it,

45
00:03:47,870 --> 00:03:49,870
the Wester Sect is better than Scarlet Sect.

46
00:03:49,870 --> 00:03:50,430
As long as

47
00:03:50,430 --> 00:03:51,560
you save my friends,

48
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,360
I could become your disciple.

49
00:03:53,430 --> 00:03:54,290
Right, Master?

50
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:56,000
You have no parents

51
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,390
and no one to rely on,

52
00:03:58,020 --> 00:03:59,950
yet you bother to stand up for them?

53
00:04:00,220 --> 00:04:01,070
I'm indebted

54
00:04:01,300 --> 00:04:02,500
to every family here.

55
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:04,260
I can't ignore them.

56
00:04:05,500 --> 00:04:06,160
It's a deal.

57
00:04:11,980 --> 00:04:12,840
It's a promise:

58
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,260
I'll be your disciple,

59
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,350
and you'll save them.

60
00:04:20,779 --> 00:04:21,390
Master.

61
00:04:24,630 --> 00:04:25,630
Put your hand on it

62
00:04:25,910 --> 00:04:27,040
and make a soul oath.

63
00:04:38,830 --> 00:04:39,830
As long as you

64
00:04:40,190 --> 00:04:41,790
personally save my friends,

65
00:04:41,909 --> 00:04:43,590
I'll be willing to be your disciple.

66
00:04:43,590 --> 00:04:44,630
If I break my promise,

67
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:45,460
my mortal body

68
00:04:45,540 --> 00:04:46,670
will disintegrate.

69
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,300
Pour me some tea

70
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,700
and then get registered at Mount Wester,

71
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:55,700
and we'll be done.

72
00:05:06,850 --> 00:05:07,850
Help!

73
00:05:14,110 --> 00:05:14,890
Thank goodness for

74
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:16,290
the talisman from Mr. Yu.

75
00:05:17,150 --> 00:05:18,210
Trying to trick me?

76
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,820
Since you want to be a coward,

77
00:05:19,940 --> 00:05:21,700
I'll provoke you to battle.

78
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,740
Using your brainpower

79
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,300
on such trifling tricks?

80
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:38,340
A talisman from the Imperial Exotic Pavilion?

81
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:40,220
Su Yu must also be nearby.

82
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:42,150
Why would he…

83
00:05:48,460 --> 00:05:49,060
Chase him!

84
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:34,350
Wei Jiu,

85
00:06:34,980 --> 00:06:37,190
trespassing the Crown Prince's bedchamber?

86
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:38,590
You've got some nerve.

87
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:40,110
Are you intent

88
00:06:39,540 --> 00:06:41,510
[Feng, immortal master]

89
00:06:40,110 --> 00:06:42,040
on going against Exotic Pavilion?

90
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:50,980
Exotic Pavilion?

91
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,330
I have zero regard

92
00:06:52,330 --> 00:06:53,330
for it.

93
00:06:54,300 --> 00:06:54,980
However,

94
00:06:55,150 --> 00:06:57,080
someone tried to find a scapegoat.

95
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,990
I don't want to be made a fool.

96
00:07:03,460 --> 00:07:04,630
My Lord, bad news.

97
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:07,070
The sovereigns of the Four Sects are here.

98
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:08,300
These old foxes

99
00:07:08,590 --> 00:07:10,020
sure are easily alerted.

100
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:11,640
Retreat.

101
00:07:22,590 --> 00:07:23,430
Ling Xiao!

102
00:07:25,190 --> 00:07:25,940
Ling Xiao!

103
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,150
Ling Xiao!

104
00:07:30,430 --> 00:07:31,110
Ling Xiao!

105
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:32,830
Ling Xiao!

106
00:07:37,150 --> 00:07:38,460
S-Sovereign Su.

107
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:41,460
You're so fast.

108
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:42,930
I didn't want to

109
00:07:43,190 --> 00:07:43,970
miss out on the tea

110
00:07:43,970 --> 00:07:44,870
from my dear disciple.

111
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:45,670
Am I right?

112
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:49,159
Although you distracted the demons away...

113
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:52,030
you didn't save the people personally.

114
00:07:52,430 --> 00:07:53,070
Is that so?

115
00:07:53,909 --> 00:07:54,980
You left in a hurry

116
00:07:55,940 --> 00:07:57,200
and forgot about this.

117
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,070
Ling Xiao.

118
00:08:00,100 --> 00:08:00,830
Give it back!

119
00:08:01,740 --> 00:08:02,400
Move aside!

120
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:14,110
The Blood Chalcedony

121
00:08:13,670 --> 00:08:15,730
[Blood Chalcedony drawing]

122
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,160
is great for nourishing the soul.

123
00:08:17,570 --> 00:08:19,900
That Blood Chalcedony can save Ling Xiao.

124
00:08:23,040 --> 00:08:23,890
If I save it,

125
00:08:24,330 --> 00:08:24,830
does it count as

126
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:26,590
me personally saving your friend?

127
00:08:26,590 --> 00:08:27,110
Yes.

128
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:28,220
Don't hurt it.

129
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:30,220
To save Ling Xiao,

130
00:08:30,610 --> 00:08:31,240
even if

131
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:32,720
Mount Wester is perilous,

132
00:08:32,820 --> 00:08:33,950
I've to give it a try.

133
00:08:37,110 --> 00:08:38,549
You are so powerful.

134
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:41,309
I won't run away.

135
00:08:42,070 --> 00:08:43,330
I'll be your disciple.

136
00:08:47,010 --> 00:08:49,700
[Mount Wester]

137
00:09:05,580 --> 00:09:08,460
[Mu Qingge, founder of Wester Sect]

138
00:09:08,300 --> 00:09:09,630
This is my Mount Wester.

139
00:09:15,070 --> 00:09:16,200
Remember the route.

140
00:09:16,470 --> 00:09:17,380
Once I get it,

141
00:09:17,630 --> 00:09:18,420
I'll flee.

142
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:20,950
What's on your mind?

143
00:09:22,550 --> 00:09:24,030
Master, you should've told me

144
00:09:24,030 --> 00:09:25,170
Mount Wester is beautiful

145
00:09:25,170 --> 00:09:26,140
with a pleasant climate.

146
00:09:26,140 --> 00:09:27,550
Since I can cultivate here,

147
00:09:27,550 --> 00:09:29,310
I feel carefree, jubilant,

148
00:09:29,340 --> 00:09:30,340
truly blessed,

149
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,260
and content.

150
00:09:32,950 --> 00:09:34,470
Your blood is in the jade tablet.

151
00:09:34,470 --> 00:09:36,860
No matter where you go, I'll be able to find you.

152
00:09:36,860 --> 00:09:38,110
Don't think about fleeing.

153
00:09:38,110 --> 00:09:40,170
You'll die if you leave Mount Wester.

154
00:09:40,250 --> 00:09:41,450
Threatening me, huh?

155
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:43,340
Guardian.

156
00:09:44,060 --> 00:09:45,160
Yu Chen told me in a letter

157
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:47,150
that you personally took in a disciple.

158
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:48,190
This is that

159
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,190
Xue Ranran?

160
00:09:52,630 --> 00:09:53,430
Settle her in.

161
00:10:03,680 --> 00:10:07,870
[Grand Hall]

162
00:10:08,630 --> 00:10:11,030
This spirit stone can identify your Spirit Roots.

163
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:13,440
Your elemental Roots determine your cultivation gift.

164
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,440
The more you have,

165
00:10:14,660 --> 00:10:15,990
the more gifted you are.

166
00:10:16,380 --> 00:10:17,300
Test it out.

167
00:10:17,740 --> 00:10:20,340
I'll go prepare the apprenticeship ceremony.

168
00:10:25,590 --> 00:10:26,700
I'm Bai Baishan

169
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:29,200
from a family of immortal cultivators.

170
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:31,200
[Bai Baishan]

171
00:10:29,260 --> 00:10:30,720
I've already been tested.

172
00:10:33,950 --> 00:10:34,810
Gold and Water;

173
00:10:35,100 --> 00:10:36,500
two Spirit Roots.

174
00:10:39,640 --> 00:10:40,570
I'm Gao Cang

175
00:10:40,600 --> 00:10:43,400
[Gao Cang]

176
00:10:40,710 --> 00:10:41,770
with an Earth Root.

177
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:44,670
My family's acquainted with Master,

178
00:10:44,740 --> 00:10:46,340
so despite my low qualifications,

179
00:10:46,340 --> 00:10:47,400
he still took me in.

180
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:49,720
[Qiu Xi'er]

181
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:49,470
I have a Fire Spirit Root.

182
00:10:49,470 --> 00:10:50,270
I'm Qiu Xi'er.

183
00:10:52,300 --> 00:10:53,550
You must be Ranran.

184
00:10:53,820 --> 00:10:54,780
I heard about another lady

185
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:55,420
joining

186
00:10:55,420 --> 00:10:56,280
upon entering.

187
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:58,400
Were you all

188
00:10:59,030 --> 00:11:00,590
taken here by force too?

189
00:11:01,300 --> 00:11:01,740
What?

190
00:11:02,380 --> 00:11:03,510
By force?

191
00:11:05,030 --> 00:11:07,070
It's the first time Master is taking disciples.

192
00:11:07,070 --> 00:11:07,920
Everyone was

193
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:09,510
busy vying for a spot.

194
00:11:09,990 --> 00:11:10,540
What?

195
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:12,150
Could it be...

196
00:11:12,170 --> 00:11:13,630
you are extraordinary

197
00:11:13,650 --> 00:11:15,310
and have all Five Spirit Roots,

198
00:11:15,310 --> 00:11:17,110
so Master was desperate for you?

199
00:11:26,630 --> 00:11:28,110
Incomplete Spirit Root?

200
00:11:28,380 --> 00:11:29,990
Not even one?

201
00:11:32,260 --> 00:11:34,630
A loser who's born incompetent

202
00:11:34,650 --> 00:11:36,700
and won't amount to much even with hard work.

203
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:37,730
How in the world

204
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:38,830
did you get

205
00:11:38,950 --> 00:11:40,300
Master to take you in?

206
00:11:41,860 --> 00:11:42,950
Are you curious?

207
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:45,630
Why don't you ask Master yourself?

208
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,780
Let's go to the discipleship ceremony.

209
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:49,780
Let's go. Come on.

210
00:11:50,470 --> 00:11:51,270
Yeah, come on.

211
00:11:51,780 --> 00:11:52,470
Look.

212
00:11:52,590 --> 00:11:53,650
The rules are here.

213
00:11:59,910 --> 00:12:02,110
You should always dress up

214
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:03,200
and look good...

215
00:12:04,370 --> 00:12:05,180
to please...

216
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:06,670
the Master?

217
00:12:07,220 --> 00:12:08,820
Don't be promiscuous,

218
00:12:09,190 --> 00:12:10,450
but more importantly,

219
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:11,930
don't be indifferent?

220
00:12:12,220 --> 00:12:15,030
You should study more about playing.

221
00:12:15,450 --> 00:12:16,430
Don't stay in the cave—

222
00:12:16,430 --> 00:12:18,430
Don't stay in the cave cultivating?

223
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:19,950
I've only heard the Heavenly Sects advocate

224
00:12:19,950 --> 00:12:20,910
detachment.

225
00:12:21,220 --> 00:12:23,220
These rules are quite interesting.

226
00:12:24,590 --> 00:12:25,340
Can you do it?

227
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:34,670
Such rules

228
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:36,640
made my eyes light up

229
00:12:36,670 --> 00:12:37,700
and spoke to my heart.

230
00:12:37,700 --> 00:12:39,560
I'll try my best to adhere to them.

231
00:12:41,990 --> 00:12:43,030
How about

232
00:12:43,300 --> 00:12:45,780
I wear a beautiful dress tomorrow

233
00:12:46,010 --> 00:12:47,470
to look good to please you?

234
00:12:50,190 --> 00:12:52,190
Every rule is illogical and absurd.

235
00:12:52,370 --> 00:12:53,250
Can't you tell?

236
00:13:01,380 --> 00:13:02,070
These rules

237
00:13:02,300 --> 00:13:04,160
were left by Mu Qingge in the past.

238
00:13:04,430 --> 00:13:05,890
Don't abide by any of them.

239
00:13:09,540 --> 00:13:10,660
Drop your blood into the jade tablet,

240
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:13,390
[Grand Hall, Mount Wester]

241
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:11,700
serve Master tea,

242
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:13,860
and get registered in the sect's records.

243
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:15,190
Then it'll be official.

244
00:13:15,420 --> 00:13:17,150
Let's start with the most powerful,

245
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,510
according to

246
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:19,650
your Spirit Roots.

247
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:30,500
Greet your master and serve tea.

248
00:13:30,960 --> 00:13:31,520
Master.

249
00:13:40,070 --> 00:13:41,600
The ceremony is completed.

250
00:13:42,470 --> 00:13:43,190
Xue Ranran.

251
00:13:43,300 --> 00:13:44,830
It's your turn to serve tea.

252
00:13:51,340 --> 00:13:52,340
Greet your master

253
00:13:52,470 --> 00:13:53,270
and serve tea.

254
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:03,340
I...

255
00:14:04,070 --> 00:14:05,600
I think my legs are numb.

256
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,690
I can't kneel down.

257
00:14:24,820 --> 00:14:25,590
Su Yishui.

258
00:14:25,930 --> 00:14:28,070
You're plotting to use me to cultivate your Core.

259
00:14:28,070 --> 00:14:29,870
Even the heavens can't stand it.

260
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:33,900
Guardian.

261
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:35,710
Why don't you reconsider it?

262
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:38,300
You've to endure the pressure of the laws of nature.

263
00:14:38,300 --> 00:14:39,510
I doubt you'd even be

264
00:14:39,510 --> 00:14:40,510
able to defy her.

265
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:47,580
Serve the tea.

266
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,130
Sor... Sorry, Master.

267
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:03,900
As they say, spilled water can't be gathered up.

268
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:05,590
Could it be that the heavens

269
00:15:05,750 --> 00:15:06,870
are hinting that

270
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:09,030
we shouldn't be master and disciple?

271
00:15:09,030 --> 00:15:09,950
Spilled water

272
00:15:11,150 --> 00:15:12,350
can't be gathered up?

273
00:15:13,950 --> 00:15:15,610
I don't believe in that logic.

274
00:15:15,740 --> 00:15:17,400
I must drink the tea you serve.

275
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:46,040
The ceremony is completed.

276
00:16:03,950 --> 00:16:05,550
You're now a Wester disciple

277
00:16:06,030 --> 00:16:06,960
and my disciple.

278
00:16:07,380 --> 00:16:08,910
Now that I'm your disciple,

279
00:16:09,260 --> 00:16:11,120
you'll have more control over me.

280
00:16:12,790 --> 00:16:15,680
[Westerly Valley, Mount Wester]

281
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:24,070
Master, this is...

282
00:16:27,420 --> 00:16:29,420
You've lived in the mortal world for 18 years.

283
00:16:29,420 --> 00:16:30,950
You're full of mortal dust.

284
00:16:31,110 --> 00:16:32,710
Get thoroughly refined here

285
00:16:32,780 --> 00:16:33,690
to cleanse your meridians

286
00:16:33,690 --> 00:16:34,620
before all else.

287
00:16:44,690 --> 00:16:45,690
Oh no. Oh no.

288
00:16:46,210 --> 00:16:47,800
Su Yishui is so sinister.

289
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:50,080
He's already ready to refine me.

290
00:16:50,850 --> 00:16:52,180
It's fire tempering...

291
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,930
I'm really going to become

292
00:16:53,930 --> 00:16:54,430
a big lump

293
00:16:54,430 --> 00:16:55,350
