00:29:35,970 --> 00:29:36,570
Don't.

601
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,160
Yishui.

602
00:29:42,280 --> 00:29:43,320
Let them go.

603
00:29:46,580 --> 00:29:47,040
You...

604
00:29:52,520 --> 00:29:53,050
Get lost!

605
00:29:57,550 --> 00:29:58,190
Let's go.

606
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:13,160
