608
00:30:24,820 --> 00:30:25,730
So eager to be the great hero

609
00:30:25,730 --> 00:30:26,560
for others?

610
00:30:27,490 --> 00:30:28,560
If anything happens to you,

611
00:30:28,560 --> 00:30:30,320
