615
00:30:35,320 --> 00:30:35,850
You...

616
00:30:36,330 --> 00:30:37,420
Just punish me now

617
00:30:37,650 --> 00:30:38,440
all you want.

618
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:47,360
Then stay here

619
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:50,410
until you've recited mantras for four hours.

620
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:57,130
I don't trust that evil man.

621
00:30:57,650 --> 00:30:58,400
He's just

622
00:30:58,400 --> 00:30:59,930
protecting his Tonic Core.

623
00:31:03,520 --> 00:31:05,160
Throughout the ice-cold ages,

624
00:31:05,160 --> 00:31:06,380
