627
00:31:17,970 --> 00:31:18,800
This is good.

628
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,600
The chill is here too.

629
00:31:20,770 --> 00:31:22,300
I'm almost at the last step.

630
00:31:27,560 --> 00:31:28,250
Ling Xiao!

631
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:31,560
I never know

632
00:31:32,010 --> 00:31:32,850
until the end.

633
00:31:33,400 --> 00:31:34,320
I can't give up.

634
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:41,000
Relinquish all desires;

635
00:31:41,210 --> 00:31:42,540
Only hard work pays off.

636
00:31:43,090 --> 00:31:44,610
Keep my rich emotions in control,

637
00:31:44,610 --> 00:31:46,010
and the universe is mine.

638
00:32:15,300 --> 00:32:16,480
The Heavenly Sects' barriers

639
00:32:16,480 --> 00:32:17,540
are so well guarded

640
00:32:17,730 --> 00:32:20,080
that I can't even detect the Fruit's energy?

641
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:20,560
My Lord.

642
00:32:20,850 --> 00:32:22,310
Why don't I send someone to sneak in—

643
00:32:22,310 --> 00:32:23,510
Do I need your advice?

644
00:32:24,290 --> 00:32:25,720
I have plenty of tricks.

645
00:32:26,130 --> 00:32:27,790
It just takes a little effort.

646
00:32:28,410 --> 00:32:29,720
Go to that girl's home

647
00:32:29,810 --> 00:32:31,010
below Mount Absolute

648
00:32:31,110 --> 00:32:32,630
and bring me something.

649
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:34,440
Yes,

650
00:32:34,470 --> 00:32:35,050
My Lord.

651
00:32:41,000 --> 00:32:42,460
He actually told me to ignore

652
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:43,570
