654
00:32:46,130 --> 00:32:47,440
No, thank you.

655
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,560
[Carefree Pavilion, Mount Wester]

656
00:32:52,460 --> 00:32:54,200
What's so strange about Guardian's sword

657
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,630
being hidden in the ruins?

658
00:32:55,630 --> 00:32:56,810
