It's a Water Mirror.

686
00:34:55,989 --> 00:34:57,760
According to the "Treasure Encyclopedia,"

687
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:58,740
it can teleport you

688
00:34:58,740 --> 00:35:00,200
to any place you want to go.

689
