696
00:36:25,850 --> 00:36:27,160
cast by Mu Qingge.

697
00:36:29,160 --> 00:36:30,090
What a pity.

698
00:36:30,720 --> 00:36:32,980
This master and disciple are really inextricably entangled.

699
00:36:32,980 --> 00:36:34,980
Their hatred lives on beyond death.

700
00:36:40,050 --> 00:36:40,710
Xue Ranran.

701
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,090
Why are you focusing on such

702
00:36:42,090 --> 00:36:42,890
nonsense now?

703
00:36:43,240 --> 00:36:44,160
I must escape

704
00:36:44,330 --> 00:36:46,130
once I get the Blood Chalcedony.

705
00:36:57,160 --> 00:36:57,990
Xue Ranran.

706
00:36:59,200 --> 00:37:00,800
What are you doing in my room?

707
00:37:02,140 --> 00:37:02,870
I was wrong.

708
00:37:03,090 --> 00:37:05,130
I shouldn't have barged into your room.

709
00:37:05,130 --> 00:37:05,650
I...

