711
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:27,810
You know Su Yu?

712
00:37:29,760 --> 00:37:30,820
How do you know him?

713
00:37:32,010 --> 00:37:33,450
He knows Young Master Yu?

714
00:37:34,890 --> 00:37:36,130
I just

715
00:37:36,650 --> 00:37:38,290
met him by chance.

716
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,640
A chance encounter,

717
00:37:42,970 --> 00:37:44,700
