733
00:39:02,220 --> 00:39:04,550
The Load-Reduction Talisman is amazing.

734
00:39:07,300 --> 00:39:09,270
Master, you're usually so boring.

735
00:39:09,450 --> 00:39:10,660
Now that you're drunk,

736
