751
00:40:20,400 --> 00:40:21,200
Little kitty.

752
00:40:21,650 --> 00:40:23,710
Do you know the way down the mountain?

753
00:40:23,960 --> 00:40:25,330
If you take me out of here,

754
00:40:25,330 --> 00:40:26,790
